data.description: Single story 5 bedroom 2 bath North Rialto home located on a quiet cul de sac. Get an additional game room not appearing on public records to the rear, updated laminated wood throughout, updated kitchen cabinets, recently painted inside, newer roof. Rear yard is a large open canvas with plenty of room for anything you may desire to add.  Property is located conveniently close to the 210 fwy, The Rialto Renaissance Marketplace with plenty of shopping and dining. The market is limited on five bedroom homes, with low taxes and no HOA, don't miss the opportunity.
